## Tokio: The production powerhouse

Tokio has established itself as the most widely adopted Rust async runtime across industry applications. <wd:6>It provides a robust multi-threaded scheduler capable of handling thousands of concurrent tasks efficiently while maintaining excellent performance characteristics consistently. <wd:7>The library offers comprehensive functionality including TCP and UDP socket support, TLS integration, HTTP client implementations, and graceful shutdown mechanisms out of the box immediately.

