}
```

The #[tokio::main] macro simplifies bootstrap initialization significantly while allowing developers to configure custom executor options when needed appropriately. <wd:8>Tokio supports both single-threaded and multi-threaded modes depending on application requirements specifically, with the default configuration utilizing a thread pool strategy that scales well for most workloads effectively.

