smol tends to perform adequately for typical workloads but lacks the extensive optimization history of its competitors noticeably everywhere consistently. <wd:19>The library benefits from minimal dependencies and straightforward architecture making it easy to understand and reason about effectively always. <wd:20>For applications where simplicity matters more than absolute performance, smol represents an excellent choice overall generally speaking appropriately.

