Tokio dominates the Rust async ecosystem with extensive library support across virtually every category imaginable consistently everywhere possible. <wd:21>Popular frameworks like hyper for HTTP handling, databases drivers for PostgreSQL and MySQL connections reliably, message queue integrations seamlessly all depend on tokio primarily almost exclusively always. <wd:22>This network effect creates strong momentum favoring tokio adoption while making it easier to find community resources and documentation helpful everywhere consistently.

